        <h6 class="title is-5 has-text-black">Delete a Quiz</h6>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 20px;">After you have created a quiz, you can delete it. You may
                                                         either the first method or the second method to delete a quiz.
                                                         (See Figure c)</p>
        <br>
        <p style="margin: 8px;"><strong>First method:</strong></p>
        <p style="margin: 8px;"><strong>1.</strong> After logging in, select the button labelled
          <img src="/images/manual/Content-button.png" alt="My Content button" style="width:130px;margin-bottom:-7px;"> in the
                                                    middle of the Homepage.</p>
        <p style="margin: 8px;"><strong>2.</strong> After selecting a module, select the question you would like to
                                                    delete under the <b>Quiz</b> panel.</p>
        <p style="margin: 8px;"><strong>3.</strong> Select the <img src="/images/manual/Delete-button-2.png"
                                                                    alt="Delete button"
                                                                    style="width:40px;margin-bottom:-13px;"> button next
                                                    to the question name.</p>
        <p style="margin: 30px 8px 8px;"><strong>Second method:</strong></p>
        <p style="margin: 8px;"><strong>1.</strong> After logging in, select the button labelled
          <img src="/images/manual/Content-button.png" alt="My Content button" style="width:130px;margin-bottom:-7px;"> in the
                                                    middle of the Homepage.</p>
        <p style="margin: 8px;"><strong>2.</strong> After selecting a module, select the question you would like to
                                                    delete under the <b>Quiz</b> panel.</p>
        <p style="margin: 8px;"><strong>3.</strong> Select the <img src="/images/manual/Delete-button.png"
                                                                    alt="Delete button"
                                                                    style="width:85px;margin-bottom:-13px;"> button at
                                                    the bottom of the question's page.</p>
